response.overview: A masked assailant targets and kills two men with ties to the drug trade, prompting a dedicated police officer to take charge of the investigation. Over the next 95 minutes, the case unravels as a standard murder mystery, offering few surprises or thrills. The main highlight for viewers is the performance of talented theatre artists, adding a touch of depth to an otherwise predictable storyline.
response.title: Prakarana Tanikha Hantadallide
